---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Integrated Aviation Management System">
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 lg:py-32 border-b border-slate-900">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_30%_30%,rgba(59,130,246,0.08),transparent_50%)]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_70%_80%,rgba(16,185,129,0.05),transparent_50%)]"></div>
    
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center relative z-10">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-blue-500/20 bg-blue-500/5 text-xs text-blue-400 font-medium mb-6">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500 animate-pulse"></span> Aligned with ICAO Annex 19 & EASA IMS Frameworks
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white mb-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-tight">
        One Management System. <br/>
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 via-indigo-400 to-emerald-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Zero Operational Silos.</span>
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
        Next-gen enterprise software unifying Safety Management (SMS) and Quality Assurance (QMS) into a single, cohesive predictive intelligence platform.
      </p>

      <div id="waitlist" class="max-w-md mx-auto p-1.5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 backdrop-blur flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 shadow-2xl shadow-slate-950">
        <input 
          type="email" 
          placeholder="Enter operator corporate email" 
          required 
          class="flex-grow bg-transparent px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white placeholder-slate-500 focus:outline-none rounded-lg focus:bg-slate-900/60 transition-all"
        />
        <a 
          href="mailto:thesafetylayer@gmail.com?subject=AviaSAFE%20Systems%20-%20Platform%20Demo%20Request" 
          class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 active:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold text-sm px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-all shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/10 shrink-0 text-center flex items-center justify-center"
        >
          Request Demo Access
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="architecture" class="py-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 border-b border-slate-900">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">The Unified Data Lifecycle</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-xl mx-auto text-sm md:text-base">
        How AviaSAFE bridges frontline hazard reporting with state-level oversight and regulatory compliance tracking.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-900 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-900/40 to-slate-950/20 relative group hover:border-slate-800/80 transition-all">
        <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm mb-6 border border-blue-500/20">01</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Identify & Assess (SMS)</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Frontline crew ingest hazard inputs directly into a centralized Master Register. Safety managers map risk severity, evaluate likelihood, and instantly deploy Corrective Action Plans (CAP).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-900 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-900/40 to-slate-950/20 relative group hover:border-slate-800/80 transition-all">
        <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm mb-6 border border-emerald-500/20">02</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Audit & Monitor (QMS)</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Seamless integration of compliance monitoring workflows. Audit findings trigger automatic cross-references into your safety data pool, resolving audit requirements before they generate systemic risk.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-900 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-900/40 to-slate-950/20 relative group hover:border-slate-800/80 transition-all">
        <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-xl bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-400 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm mb-6 border border-purple-500/20">03</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Global SPI Alignment</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Local Safety Performance Indicators automatically align with state programs and high-level regulatory tracking criteria—including critical metrics for LOC-I, CFIT, and Runway Excursions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="modules" class="py-20 bg-slate-950">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-slate-950 border border-slate-800/60 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12">
        <div class="lg:w-1/2">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-400 block mb-3">Enterprise Cloud Topology</span>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Scalable Domain Architecture</h2>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Engineered using a flexible micro-app setup. Your public marketing workspace stays lightweight and lightning fast on the root infrastructure, while specific heavy-duty regulatory engines run securely isolated across individual modules.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
              <code class="text-xs text-blue-400 font-mono bg-blue-950/50 border border-blue-900/40 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">app.aviasafesystems.com</code>
              <span>Unified Dashboard Core</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
              <code class="text-xs text-emerald-400 font-mono bg-emerald-950/50 border border-emerald-900/40 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">sms.aviasafesystems.com</code>
              <span>Safety Assurance & Hazard Logic</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-300">
              <code class="text-xs text-purple-400 font-mono bg-purple-950/50 border border-purple-900/40 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">qms.aviasafesystems.com</code>
              <span>Compliance Monitoring & Quality Audits</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 w-full bg-slate-950/60 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 p-6 font-mono text-xs text-slate-400 shadow-inner">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-slate-900 pb-3 mb-4">
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/40"></span>
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/40"></span>
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/40"></span>
            <span class="text-slate-500 ml-2">aviasafe-system-manifest.json</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-blue-400">&#123;"platform": "AviaSAFE Systems",</p>
          <p class="text-slate-50">&nbsp;&nbsp;"compliance": ["ICAO Annex 19", "EASA IMS"],</p>
          <p class="text-slate-50">&nbsp;&nbsp;"modules": &#123;</p>
          <p class="text-emerald-400">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"sms_core": "active",</p>
          <p class="text-purple-400">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"qms_integration": "pending_phase_2"</p>
          <p class="text-slate-50">&nbsp;&nbsp;&#125;,</p>
          <p class="text-slate-50">&nbsp;&nbsp;"deployment": "Cloudflare Pages + Isolated Secure App Nodes"</p>
          <p class="text-blue-400">&#125;</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
